A suggestion for the next release:

It may be better to not throw an error on a temperature-specified
equilibrium solve if the temperature exceeds the polynomial fit range.
 It may be best to go ahead with the solution, and leave it up to the
user to check validity of the temperature limits.

Thanks,

James
